config PANICOS_DEVICE_RG353P
	bool "anbernic/rg353p (Rockchip RK3566)"
	select PANICOS_SOC_ROCKCHIP_RK3566
	help
	  Anbernic RG353P — Rockchip RK3566 (quad-core Cortex-A55), 1 GB LPDDR4.
	  Uses the anbernic-rgxx3-rk3566 U-Boot defconfig (auto-detects device
	  via DTSOC at runtime, covers the whole RGxx3 Anbernic family).

	  Kernel: Linux 7.0.1 mainline + ROCKNIX patches.
	  Default DTB: rk3566-anbernic-rg353p.dtb (in-tree upstream).
